    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，当收到more input时，NeedMore会自循环，保持在当前状态继续等待后续数据。另外，如果收到EOF或者数据complete了，就要转到Complete状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了NeedMore到自身的循环，标注more input，还有NeedMore到Complete的转移，标注EOF/complete。那异常情况呢？比如数据格式出错？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NeedMore",
        "Complete",
